gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Knicks 108, Nets 103
gameRecap.excerpt: The Knicks defeat the Nets, 108-103.  Jalen Brunson (30 points, four assists) and Julius Randle (30 points, nine rebounds, seven assists) combined for 60 points for the Knicks in the victory, while Mikal Bridges tallied 36 points (seven 3PM), five rebounds and five assists for the Nets in the losing effort.  The Knicks improve to 27-17 on the season, while the Nets fall to 17-26.
